               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17870418-52-person468">
                  MARY
                   TAYLOR
               <interp inst="t17870418-52-person468" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870418-52-person468" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870418-52-person468" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am servant to the prosecutor; on the 23d of March last I was in the parlour, and had rubbed the things mentioned in the indictment, which lay on a little sideboard; the street-door was open, and the prisoner came in softly, and took them; he did not see me; he put them in his pocket, and put a mug under his coat; I ran after him, and he turned round and hit me with the mug on the head, and again on the side; he ran away, and I lost him; he was taken the next morning; the things were never found; I am sure he is the person.</p>
               <p>
            
